@startuml ClassDiagram_Facade
title Class Diagram — Facade Pattern

skinparam classBackgroundColor White
skinparam classBorderColor DarkBlue
skinparam classArrowColor DarkBlue
skinparam stereotypeCBackgroundColor LightYellow
skinparam stereotypeIBackgroundColor LightBlue
skinparam noteBackgroundColor LightYellow
skinparam noteBorderColor DarkBlue

' ── Client ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class FormMain {
    - r_FacebookService : IFacebookService
    --
    - displayUserInfo() : void
    - loadFriends() : void
    - loadRecentPosts() : void
    - loadAlbumsIntoGrid() : void
}
note top of FormMain : **Pattern role: Client**\nNever calls FacebookService (SDK) directly.\nAll access goes through IFacebookService.

' ── Facade Interface ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

interface IFacebookService {
    + LoggedInUser : User <<get>>
    + Login(i_AppId : string) : LoginResult
    + ConnectWithToken(i_Token : string) : LoginResult
    + Logout() : void
    + GetFriends() : List<User>
    + GetAlbums() : List<Album>
    + GetRecentPosts(i_MaxCount : int) : List<Post>
    + GetPhotosFromAlbum(i_Album : Album) : List<Photo>
    + PostStatus(i_Content : string) : void
    + UploadPhotoToAlbum(i_Album : Album, i_FilePath : string) : void
}
note top of IFacebookService : **Pattern role: Facade Interface**\nSimplified contract that hides\nall SDK complexity from the client.

' ── Facade ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class FacebookManager {
    - m_LoginResult : LoginResult
    --
    + LoggedInUser : User <<get>>
    + Login(i_AppId : string) : LoginResult
    + ConnectWithToken(i_Token : string) : LoginResult
    + Logout() : void
    + GetFriends() : List<User>
    + GetAlbums() : List<Album>
    + GetRecentPosts(i_MaxCount : int) : List<Post>
    + GetPhotosFromAlbum(i_Album : Album) : List<Photo>
    + PostStatus(i_Content : string) : void
    + UploadPhotoToAlbum(i_Album : Album, i_FilePath : string) : void
}
note right of FacebookManager : **Pattern role: Facade**\nHides the FacebookWrapper SDK.\nTranslates simple calls into\ncomplex SDK operations.

' ── Subsystem (external SDK) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

class FacebookService <<external>> {
    + {static} s_CollectionLimit : int
    --
    + {static} Login(appId : string, permissions : string[]) : LoginResult
    + {static} Connect(token : string) : LoginResult
    + {static} LogoutWithUI() : void
}

class LoginResult <<external>> {
    + AccessToken : string
    + ErrorMessage : string
    + LoggedInUser : User
}
note right of FacebookService : **Pattern role: Subsystem**\nComplex external SDK that the\nFacade simplifies and hides.

' ── Relationships ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

FormMain "1" ..> "1" IFacebookService : <<uses>>
FacebookManager ..|> IFacebookService
FacebookManager "1" ..> "1" FacebookService : <<uses>>
FacebookManager "1" o-- "0..1" LoginResult : aggregates

@enduml
